都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c964d2f946992725ec7605cf3204c3ec239b3694","tid":770041,"uid":144372,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T17:00:53.000Z","msg":"2016年太陽花學運之後嘅總統選舉<br />\n全台灣都係民進黨大勝<br />\n國民黨冇1個地方得票過半<br />\n<br />\n但係金門泛藍加埋仲係得票82%<br />\n香港啲新移民投建制派都冇咁高比例<br />\n國民黨24,327（66.10%）\t<br />\n民進黨6,626（18.00%）<br />\n親民黨\t5,852（15.90%）"},{"pid":"a7892166d80333bbf19c6bb4800499f196cf7629","tid":770041,"uid":169310,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"quote":{"pid":"bf76f4cf356f3d7f7550e1b0c6a255847e12660a","tid":770041,"uid":163954,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"6bffbb44db87d2e329509f4e573f30f6e6ee9f4d","tid":770041,"uid":144372,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"quote":{"pid":"070a5c801994831a32aafb79dcc030c029d42cc8","tid":770041,"uid":75232,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T16:45:28.000Z","msg":"啲輸水管夠唔夠闊俾大陸士兵潛去金門攻打台灣？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T16:54:32.000Z","msg":"金門洗撚攻打<br />\n公投回歸都實贏"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T16:57:14.000Z","msg":"可以連金門係邊都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T17:01:58.000Z","msg":"金門係一個好過引ga地方，廈門坐船幾個鐘就到，一上到去，同台灣本土真係好似，金門中心金門車站，7-11，所有野同本土都好似，有機場有碼頭，但同廈門只係隔離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚過引"},{"pid":"adcf58c2d8cb0f2359087985b4feed918f555cfd","tid":770041,"uid":46151,"like":65,"dislike":0,"score":65,"quote":{"pid":"c7310eb4225cf4b167b46038c0062d973af26b59","tid":770041,"uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":9,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T16:45:32.000Z","msg":"台仔唔問下東江屎水多少錢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T17:02:06.000Z","msg":"兩條女都俾人姦緊<br />\n竟然有一個同第二個講你未算最慘 我連屎眼都俾人開緊埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/h